fields.description:
Use Jinja2 template syntax. Each line becomes a row. Use | or tab to separate columns.

Available Variables:
- {{ company }} - Company name
- {{ doctype }} - Document type identifier or filename
- {{ report_name }} - Report title (e.g., "General Ledger") when available
- {{ user_fullname }} - Current user's full name
- {{ date }} - Current date (datetime.date)
- {{ time }} - Current time (datetime.time)
- {{ now }} - Current datetime
- {{ frappe }} - Frappe object for advanced scripting

Tips:
- A blank separator row is automatically inserted after the letterhead
- You can format dates/times via strftime, e.g., {{ date.strftime('%B %d, %Y') }}

Examples:
1. Simple single column:
{{ company }}
Document Export

2. Multi-column (using | separator):
{{ company }} | {{ report_name or doctype }} | {{ date.strftime('%B %d, %Y') }}

3. Multi-column (using tab separator):
{{ company }}	{{ user_fullname }}	{{ time.strftime('%I:%M %p') }}

4. With conditional logic:
{% if report_name %}
Report: {{ report_name }}
{% else %}
Export: {{ doctype }}
{% endif %}

fields.default:
TEMPLATE GUIDE:

1. Each line = one row in the export
2. Use | or tab to separate columns
3. Empty lines are ignored
4. A blank separator row is automatically added after the letterhead

AVAILABLE VARIABLES:
- {{ company }} - Company name
- {{ doctype }} - Document type identifier or filename
- {{ report_name }} - Report title (e.g., General Ledger), when available
- {{ user_fullname }} - Current user's full name
- {{ date }} - Current date (datetime.date)
- {{ time }} - Current time (datetime.time)
- {{ now }} - Current datetime object
- {{ frappe }} - Frappe object for advanced scripting

DATE/TIME FORMATTING:
- Use strftime, e.g., {{ date.strftime('%B %d, %Y') }} or {{ time.strftime('%I:%M %p') }}

EXAMPLES:

Example 1 - Simple header:
{{ company }}
Export Report

Example 2 - Multi-column with pipe:
{{ company }} | {{ report_name or doctype }} | {{ date.strftime('%B %d, %Y') }}

Example 3 - Multi-column with tab:
{{ company }}	{{ user_fullname }}	{{ time.strftime('%H:%M:%S') }}

Example 4 - With conditional logic:
{% if report_name %}
Report: {{ report_name }}
{% else %}
Export: {{ doctype }}
{% endif %}

Example 5 - Complex template:
{{ company }}
{{ report_name or doctype }} Export
Generated on: {{ date.strftime('%B %d, %Y') }} at {{ time.strftime('%I:%M %p') }}
Exported by: {{ user_fullname }}
